casebody.data:
The State ex rel. Hampton, Appellant, v. Ohio Adult Parole Authority, Appellee.

[Cite as State ex rel. Hampton v. Ohio Adult Parole Auth. (1992), 65 Ohio St.3d 132.]

(No. 92-1272 — Submitted October 13, 1992 — Decided November 18, 1992.) Rick Hampton, pro se. Lee I. Fisher, Attorney General, and Donald A. Cataldi, Assistant Attorney General, for appellee.

The judgment of the court of appeals is affirmed.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
